title: Choko Moko
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Russian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Gluten-free bakery making baked goods that are all vegan suitable (cakes, donuts cookies, chocolate eclairs). The restaurant portion offers breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Most restaurant menu items can be made vegan upon request.
